{"tid":1785841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和理shop開始要洗版宣傳","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T08:26:01.000Z","uid":264246,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f549d8156050e7486638bbd368fd78143b528d03","tid":1785841,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"大家都知道水軍入撚哂黎啦,區選前都無咁誇張,區選後多撚到<br />\n大家要知道若果果個禮拜如果無遊行既話,和理shop就一定要<br />\n呼籲大家所有肯出去既就一齊出去<br />\n同埋真心當你係入面夠人塞就已經到達左我地既目的<br />\n真係唔洗有人冒險幫你裝修<br />\n要將和你shop變到好似以前60 70年代d人食完飯無野做<br />\n就落去一齊塞<br />\n呢d先叫做將抗爭混入日常<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再乜春靜靜雞<br />\n呢樣野係一定要做<br />\n你可以話都拉左好多人<br />\n但係點解明知佢砌唔撚入,都仲要無啦啦沖入黎鳩拉你<br />\n希望大家都平安和平<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"efb57131460da25cc2297b904f47655c1f4d9143","tid":1785841,"uid":75195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7586c04db99037ed211ea1d4862481c274304dae","tid":1785841,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1元旦大遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8cUMgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8cUMgZ.jpg&h=dd131fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qF3EB1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qF3EB1.jpg&h=981a21a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5GnaJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5GnaJH.jpg&h=8d5141c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeRnaJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeRnaJJ.jpg&h=513a7d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxgqSW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt